[{"index": 0, "text": "like what was like the hardest thing for y 'all when you think back?", "start": 0.38, "end": 3.652, "zh": "回想起来,你们觉得最难的是什么?", "zh_hant": "回想起來,你們覺得最難的是什麼?"}, {"index": 1, "text": "What was like the biggest culture shock?", "start": 3.652, "end": 5.183, "zh": "最大的文化冲击是什么?", "zh_hant": "最大的文化衝擊是什麼?"}, {"index": 2, "text": "Or what was like one of the hardest things?", "start": 5.183, "end": 7.204, "zh": "或者说,最难的事情之一是什么?", "zh_hant": "或者說,最難的事情之一是什麼?"}, {"index": 3, "text": "Or was there ever a moment where you said something that was like the wrong word in the worst way?", "start": 7.904, "end": 13.627, "zh": "有没有那种,你说错话说得特别离谱的时刻?", "zh_hant": "有沒有那種,你說錯話說得特別離譜的時刻?"}, {"index": 4, "text": "Yeah, because you know Korean…", "start": 13.767, "end": 16.608, "zh": "对,因为你知道韩语……", "zh_hant": "對,因為你知道韓語……"}, {"index": 5, "text": "It has a lot of like Hanzha.", "start": 17.589, "end": 19.33, "zh": "里面有很多汉字词。", "zh_hant": "裡面有很多漢字詞。"}, {"index": 6, "text": "It's a word that came from like Chinese something.", "start": 19.85, "end": 23.252, "zh": "就是那种源自中文的词。", "zh_hant": "就是那種源自中文的詞。"}, {"index": 7, "text": "So I just mix them up a lot when I first time in Korea.", "start": 23.252, "end": 26.513, "zh": "所以我刚到韩国的时候,总是把它们搞混。", "zh_hant": "所以我剛到韓國的時候,總是把它們搞混。"}, {"index": 8, "text": "But actually the…", "start": 27.254, "end": 28.574, "zh": "不过其实……", "zh_hant": "不過其實……"}, {"index": 9, "text": "You were talking about the culture shock.", "start": 29.615, "end": 31.636, "zh": "你刚才说到文化冲击。", "zh_hant": "你剛才說到文化衝擊。"}, {"index": 10, "text": "It's super different from I think from between China and Korea.", "start": 32.156, "end": 36.448, "zh": "我觉得中国和韩国之间真的很不一样。", "zh_hant": "我覺得中國和韓國之間真的很不一樣。"}, {"index": 11, "text": "Because you know in our country…", "start": 36.448, "end": 38.399, "zh": "因为在我们国家……", "zh_hant": "因為在我們國家……"}, {"index": 12, "text": "The like…", "start": 38.419, "end": 39.44, "zh": "就是那种……", "zh_hant": "就是那種……"}, {"index": 13, "text": "Unnie, dongsaeng…", "start": 39.561, "end": 41.081, "zh": "unnie(姐姐)、dongsaeng(弟弟妹妹)这种称呼……", "zh_hant": "unnie(姐姐)、dongsaeng(弟弟妹妹)這種稱呼……"}, {"index": 14, "text": "We don't have these things.", "start": 41.281, "end": 43.582, "zh": "我们没有这些东西。", "zh_hant": "我們沒有這些東西。"}, {"index": 15, "text": "So…", "start": 43.582, "end": 43.922, "zh": "所以……", "zh_hant": "所以……"}, {"index": 16, "text": "And for me, my personality…", "start": 44.183, "end": 45.923, "zh": "而且就我的性格来说……", "zh_hant": "而且就我的性格來說……"}, {"index": 17, "text": "I'm really you know outgoing and I just see everybody as my friends.", "start": 45.923, "end": 50.086, "zh": "我是那种很外向的人,我觉得所有人都是我的朋友。", "zh_hant": "我是那種很外向的人,我覺得所有人都是我的朋友。"}, {"index": 18, "text": "So I don't like like…", "start": 50.086, "end": 51.056, "zh": "所以我不太喜欢……", "zh_hant": "所以我不太喜歡……"}, {"index": 19, "text": "Oh I have to listen to the sisters sometimes.", "start": 51.056, "end": 53.947, "zh": "哦,有时候还得听姐姐(unnie)的话。", "zh_hant": "哦,有時候還得聽姐姐(unnie)的話。"}, {"index": 20, "text": "So very first time, I just couldn't receive that.", "start": 54.148, "end": 58.27, "zh": "所以刚开始的时候,我完全接受不了。", "zh_hant": "所以剛開始的時候,我完全接受不了。"}, {"index": 21, "text": "Because the SINGEI team, they asked me to…", "start": 58.27, "end": 60.681, "zh": "因为SINGEI团队让我……", "zh_hant": "因為SINGEI團隊讓我……"}, {"index": 22, "text": "You have to listen to unnies.", "start": 60.681, "end": 63.192, "zh": "你必须听unnie(姐姐)们的话。", "zh_hant": "你必須聽unnie(姐姐)們的話。"}, {"index": 23, "text": "Sunbae.", "start": 64.483, "end": 64.993, "zh": "还有sunbae(前辈)。", "zh_hant": "還有sunbae(前輩)。"}, {"index": 24, "text": "I was like, why?", "start": 64.993, "end": 65.883, "zh": "我当时就想,为什么?", "zh_hant": "我當時就想,為什麼?"}, {"index": 25, "text": "do I have to do it?", "start": 65.883, "end": 67.034, "zh": "为什么我非得这么做?", "zh_hant": "為什麼我非得這麼做?"}, {"index": 26, "text": "Because I have my own personality.", "start": 67.034, "end": 68.765, "zh": "因为我有自己的个性。", "zh_hant": "因為我有自己的個性。"}, {"index": 27, "text": "I'm Wookie.", "start": 68.765, "end": 69.855, "zh": "我是Wookie。", "zh_hant": "我是Wookie。"}, {"index": 28, "text": "But why I have to…", "start": 70.115, "end": 71.146, "zh": "但为什么我非得……", "zh_hant": "但為什麼我非得……"}, {"index": 29, "text": "Because I lived in my hometown for about 20 years.", "start": 71.146, "end": 76.508, "zh": "因为我在家乡生活了大概二十年。", "zh_hant": "因為我在家鄉生活了大概二十年。"}, {"index": 30, "text": "But now you ask me to change it?", "start": 76.508, "end": 79.11, "zh": "现在你却让我改变?", "zh_hant": "現在你卻讓我改變?"}, {"index": 31, "text": "I said, no.", "start": 79.11, "end": 79.921, "zh": "我说,不。", "zh_hant": "我說,不。"}, {"index": 32, "text": "I won't do it.", "start": 79.921, "end": 80.302, "zh": "我不会这么做的。", "zh_hant": "我不會這麼做的。"}, {"index": 33, "text": "Yeah it was hard.", "start": 80.302, "end": 81.212, "zh": "是啊,那时候真的很难。", "zh_hant": "是啊,那時候真的很難。"}, {"index": 34, "text": "Do you have moments now where you have a dongsaeng and you're like, hey.", "start": 81.212, "end": 84.025, "zh": "那你现在有dongsaeng(弟弟妹妹)的时候,会不会也这样对他们说?", "zh_hant": "那你現在有dongsaeng(弟弟妹妹)的時候,會不會也這樣對他們說?"}, {"index": 35, "text": "I never do that.", "start": 84.505, "end": 85.286, "zh": "我从来不会那样。", "zh_hant": "我從來不會那樣。"}, {"index": 36, "text": "You don't do that?", "start": 85.286, "end": 85.796, "zh": "你不会那样?", "zh_hant": "你不會那樣?"}, {"index": 37, "text": "I never do that.", "start": 85.796, "end": 86.227, "zh": "我从来不会。", "zh_hant": "我從來不會。"}, {"index": 38, "text": "Because everybody's chingu.", "start": 86.227, "end": 87.378, "zh": "因为大家都是chingu(朋友)。", "zh_hant": "因為大家都是chingu(朋友)。"}, {"index": 39, "text": "Yes.", "start": 87.378, "end": 87.768, "zh": "是的。", "zh_hant": "是的。"}, {"index": 40, "text": "Everybody's chingu.", "start": 87.768, "end": 88.829, "zh": "大家都是chingu(朋友)。", "zh_hant": "大家都是chingu(朋友)。"}, {"index": 41, "text": "Okay.", "start": 88.829, "end": 89.329, "zh": "好吧。", "zh_hant": "好吧。"}, {"index": 42, "text": "That's good.", "start": 89.33, "end": 89.96, "zh": "这样很好。", "zh_hant": "這樣很好。"}, {"index": 43, "text": "I'm that kind of style.", "start": 89.96, "end": 90.841, "zh": "我就是这种风格。", "zh_hant": "我就是這種風格。"}, {"index": 44, "text": "That's good.", "start": 90.841, "end": 91.241, "zh": "这样很好。", "zh_hant": "這樣很好。"}, {"index": 45, "text": "But…", "start": 91.241, "end": 91.631, "zh": "但是……", "zh_hant": "但是……"}, {"index": 46, "text": "Okay.", "start": 91.712, "end": 93.173, "zh": "好吧。", "zh_hant": "好吧。"}, {"index": 47, "text": "I'm kind of kkondae.", "start": 93.293, "end": 95.585, "zh": "我算是有点kkondae(倚老卖老)。", "zh_hant": "我算是有點kkondae(倚老賣老)。"}, {"index": 48, "text": "Sorry.", "start": 95.585, "end": 96.176, "zh": "抱歉。", "zh_hant": "抱歉。"}, {"index": 49, "text": "I was like…", "start": 96.516, "end": 97.077, "zh": "我当时就……", "zh_hant": "我當時就……"}, {"index": 50, "text": "The first time I met him, he was like…", "start": 97.077, "end": 98.558, "zh": "我第一次见到他的时候,他说……", "zh_hant": "我第一次見到他的時候,他說……"}, {"index": 51, "text": "I'm Bonnie.", "start": 99.299, "end": 100.259, "zh": "我是Bonnie。", "zh_hant": "我是Bonnie。"}, {"index": 52, "text": "Hello.", "start": 100.42, "end": 101.04, "zh": "你好。", "zh_hant": "你好。"}]